{"about_the_game":"<strong>VALHALL</strong> is a blend of multiple genres, combining first &amp; third person directional physical combat slasher with a survival experience set in a brutal world of Vikings.<br><br><strong>Open World Survival</strong><br>Build and defend your settlement. Gather resources, look for food, protect yourself from wildlife and nature. Every tree can be chopped down. Craft weapons and tools. Prepare for battles with other Vikings and creatures. Raid and loot other camps.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/908740/extras/SurvGIF2.gif?t=1724321658\" /><br><br><strong>Physically Simulated Combat </strong><br>Control the direction and type of your attacks and blocks with a fluid, weighty, and dynamic Viking combat system. Dodge, slide, and execute various special movements.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/908740/extras/Combat.gif?t=1724321658\" /><br><br><strong>Battle Arena</strong><br>Enter the arena of endless battle and fight against waves of foes with increasing strength in this challenging game game. Carve out a path of glory with each triumph, and prove your worth to the gods as you strive to claim the legendary Mjolnir.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/908740/extras/ArenaGIF.gif?t=1724321658\" /><br><br><strong>Wield Mjolnir</strong><br>Dominate your foes by teaching them how to fly. Shake the ground beneath them. Take control of your attacks by adjusting the distance of your Mjolnir throws in real-time with the actual swing of your mouse.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/908740/extras/MjolnirGIF.gif?t=1724321658\" /><br><br><strong>Deathmatch</strong><br>Engage in a free-for-all battle against other warriors.<br><br>More in development.<br><br>Sk\u00e5l!","background